metadata.name: Caribbean Architectural Alphabet 2022
metadata.description:
For the 2nd year in a row, I have illustrated all the letters and numerals of the alphabet in the style of Caribbean Architecture. 

Anyone that bids on this piece will receive an airdropped NFT with a custom word of their choice written out using this alphabet.

The collector of this piece will receive print number 1 from the limited edition run of prints of this piece.
